title: Static Analysis

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION.description: Access fine location sources, such as the Global Positioning System on the phone, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine where you are and may consume additional battery power.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.USE_BIOMETRIC.description: Allows an app to use device supported biometric modalities.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.AUTHENTICATE_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to use the account authenticator capabilities of the Account Manager, including creating accounts as well as obtaining and setting their passwords.

android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to access the list of accounts known by the phone.

android.permission.MANAGE_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to perform operations like adding and removing accounts and deleting their password.

android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATIO.description: Access coarse location sources, such as the mobile network database, to determine an approximate phone location, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine approximately where you are.

com.amazon.device.messaging.permission.R.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

com.huawei.android.launcher.permission.W.description: Allows an application to modify the system's settings data. Malicious applications can corrupt your system's configuration.

com.oppo.launcher.permission.WRITE_SETTI.description: Allows an application to modify the system's settings data. Malicious applications can corrupt your system's configuration.

manifest_analysis.title:
Service (androidx.work.impl.background.systemjob.SystemJobService) is Protected by a permission, but the protection level of the permission should be checked.
Permission: android.permission.BIND_JOB_SERVICE
[android:exported=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: A Service is found to be shared with other apps on the device therefore leaving it accessible to any other application on the device. It is protected by a permission which is not defined in the analysed application. As a result, the protection level of the permission should be checked where it is defined. If it is set to normal or dangerous, a malicious application can request and obtain the permission and interact with the component. If it is set to signature, only applications signed with the same certificate can obtain the permission.
manifest_analysis.name: is Protected by a permission, but the protection level of the permission should be checked.[android:exported=true]

"post_creation_guidelines_intro_text_line" : "Com o Newsroom, você pode se manter atualizado, participar de conversas sobre assuntos atuais e fazer parte de comunidades interessadas em notícias."

"post_creation_guidelines_negative_text_line1" : "Fazer spam, como por exemplo postar comentários em grandes quantidades para promover um produto/serviço ou postar o mesmo comentário de forma repetida em um tópico."

"post_creation_guidelines_negative_text_line4" : "O Newsroom não é uma plataforma para: - conteúdo pornográfico, violento ou perturbador - conteúdo que promove a violência ou faz uso de discurso de ódio - conteúdo que contém informações pessoais ou confidenciais - Spam."
"post_creation_guidelines_negative_text_line5" : "Criar ou fazer upload de conteúdo que infrinja qualquer direito autoral, marca comercial ou patente."
"post_creation_guidelines_positive_text_line1" : "Compartilhe conteúdo nas paradas que você segue."
"post_creation_guidelines_positive_text_line2" : "Poste nas paradas mais relevantes e apropriadas."
"post_creation_guidelines_positive_text_line3" : "Poste uma mesma história em várias paradas, desde que o conteúdo faça sentido para o tópico."
"post_creation_guidelines_positive_text_line4" : "Lembre-se de que há uma pessoa do outro lado da tela. Interaja com outros usuários com educação e respeito."
"post_creation_guidelines_positive_text_line5" : "Respeite as opiniões e crenças das outras pessoas."
"post_creation_guidelines_positive_text_line6" : "Contribua para a comunidade comentando e curtindo as notícias."

"canvass_violation_3" : "Nezverejňujte telefónne čísla, e-mailové alebo poštové adresy či informácie o kreditných kartách. Pomáha to chrániť vaše osobné informácie, ako aj informácie ostatných používateľov."

"canvass_violation_4" : "Nekopírujte a nezverejňujte materiál, ochranné známky alebo duševné vlastníctvo iných používateľov – je to nelegálne. Patrí sem aj vystrihovanie a prilepovanie obsahu z iných webových stránok (v komentároch by ste mali uvádzať vlastné myšlienky)."

"canvass_guideline_account_text" : "Yahoo залишає за собою право видалити будь-який коментар, який не відповідає нашим рекомендаціям чи умовам надання послуг, і припинити дію облікового запису Yahoo (включно з електронною поштою) через порушення."

"canvass_guideline_header" : "Будемо вдячні, якщо ви допоможете забезпечити зручність і безпеку для всіх, хто спілкується через систему Yahoo. Перш ніж опублікувати коментар, перегляньте кілька корисних рекомендацій."
"canvass_violation_1" : "Не публікуйте вміст, який є грубим, непристойним, образливим або неприйнятним з іншої причини."

"canvass_violation_2" : "Коментарі не повинні представляти собою переслідування, жорстоке ставлення або загрозу чиєїсь безпеці чи власності. Вони також не повинні містити неправдиві твердження та наклеп або використовуватися для імітації чужої особистості."
"canvass_violation_3" : "Не публікуйте номери телефонів, фізичні та електронні адреси, дані кредитних карток. Це допоможе захистити ваші особисті відомості та відомості інших людей."

"canvass_violation_4" : "Не копіюйте матеріали, торговельні марки та інтелектуальну власність інших осіб — це незаконно. Зокрема, не вставляйте в публікації вміст з інших веб-сайтів (коментарі мають виражати вашу особисту думку)."
"canvass_violation_5" : "Публікування HTML-кодів, вірусів та інших шкідливих кодів є порушенням умов надання послуг Yahoo."
"canvass_violation_6" : "Yahoo відмовляється від будь-яких зобов’язань чи відповідальності відносно коментарів, опублікованих користувачами."

"canvass_violation_4" : "Nemojte kopirati ni objavljivati tuđe materijale, zaštitne znakove ni intelektualno vlasništvo – to je zabranjeno zakonom. To obuhvaća izrezivanje i lijepljenje sadržaja s drugih web-mjesta (komentari moraju biti vaše izvorne misli)."

"canvass_guideline_header" : "Rádi bych vás požádali o pomoc, aby Yahoo zůstalo příjemným a bezpečným místem pro komunikaci s ostatními. Než publikujete komentář, projděte si několik pokynů, aby váš příspěvek byl pro všechny užitečný."

"canvass_violation_3" : "Nezveřejňujte telefonní čísla, e-mailové nebo poštovní adresy nebo údaje o platebních kartách. Tím chráníte své osobní údaje i údaje dalších osob."

"canvass_violation_4" : "Nekopírujte a nepublikujte materiály, ochranné známky nebo duševní vlastnictví jiných osob – je to nezákonné. Týká se to i kopírování obsahu z jiných webů (komentáře by měly obsahovat vaše původní myšlenky)."

playstore_details.title: Yahoo News: National, Breaking & Live
playstore_details.description:
Yahoo-HuffPost News Network is now the #1 US Digital News destination!
(Source: Comscore Media Metrix ® Multi-Platform, News/Information Category, Total Audience Unique Visitors, October 2019)

Focus on what’s important with the newest version of the Yahoo News app. Now you can customize your news with your favorite topics and publishers, while our expert editors curate top stories from trusted sources. It’s time to reframe your newsfeed around what matters to you. 

‣ News from trusted sources like The New York Times, USA Today, TIME, Politico, AP, Fox News and more.

‣ The 360 examines important topics from a variety of perspectives.

‣ Customize topics and publishers to personalize your newsfeed.

‣ Search across all news sources to easily find what you’re looking for.

‣ Watch exclusive and live video for trending news, press conferences, the day's soundbites and more.

‣ Expert editors curate the day’s top stories. Get premium original content like our Skullduggery podcast, highlighting scandals and investigations in the Trump era.

‣ Never miss an important story with breaking news alerts across national and global news.

‣ Get 2020 election coverage from across the political spectrum.
